The '''House of Antilles''' hailed from [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], and, along with the [[House of Organa/Legends|House of Organa]], was one of the most influential families of that planet. Both families struggled during the [[Alderaan Ascendancy Contention]], which ended with a marriage between the houses.

==Known members==
*[[Bail Antilles/Legends|Bail Antilles]], [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] of Alderaan
**[[Bail Antilles's wife|His wife]]
*[[Breha Organa/Legends|Breha Organa]], born Breha Antilles, [[Monarch of Alderaan|Queen of Alderaan]] and wife of Senator [[Bail Prestor Organa/Legends|Bail Prestor Organa]]
**Her sister [[Deara Antilles]]
*[[Raymus Antilles/Legends|Raymus Antilles]], captain of the [[Sundered Heart/Legends|''Sundered Heart'']] and later the [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']]
**His niece [[Corla Metonae/Legends|Corla Metonae]]

